    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Qualifier used for a work by an unknown creator who appears to be associated with the named artist, he or she is living at the same time as the named artist, and probably had some contact with him or her, but not is necessarily his or her pupil.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
